If you want to build critical chance you have:
{{item:3508}} {{item:3031}} {{item:3046}} {{item:3094}} {{item:3085}} {{item:3087}} {{item:3078}} 

Meanwhile, as an AP, if you want CDR you have:
{{item:3092}} {{item:3100}} {{item:3165}} {{item:3174}} {{item:3152}} {{item:3115}}

And, from there, there is one item (Nashor's Tooth) that can't be used by mages, only AP fighters like Diana, other one that can be used only by two or three (Lich Bane) and FQC that RIOT doesn't want them to build. AD champions have far more options which are enough to make sure everyone has the item they need.
